Walaa Issam ElBoushi (nakwa: Wala'a, Walla, Isam, Essam, al-Bushi, al- Boushi, el-Boushi; Arabic) bụ onye Sudanese na-eme ihe ike nke ghọrọ Minista Sudan nke Ndị Ntorobịa na Egwuregwu na mbido Septemba 2019 na Kọmitii Mgbanwe nke Praịm Minista Abdalla Hamdok, n'oge mgbanwe Sudan na 2019 na ọchịchị onye kwuo uche ya.
A mụrụ Al-Boushi na 1986 na Wad Madani
O nwere nzere masta na Advanced Engineering Mechanics site na Imperial College London.
Al-Boushi tinyere aka na mmegide gọọmentị na Sudan n'oge onye isi ala Omar al-Bashir, onye a chụpụrụ n'ọchịchị Sudan n'April 2019.
Na mbido Septemba 2019, al-Boushi ghọrọ Minista Sudan nke Ndị Ntorobịa na Egwuregwu na Kọmitii Mgbanwe nke Praịm Minista Abdalla Hamdok, n'oge mgbanwe Sudan nke 2019 gaa na ọchịchị onye kwuo uche ya
Ndị isi nwanyị ndị ọzọ nke Sudan n'oge mgbanwe ahụ gụnyere Chief Justice Nemat Abdullah Khair, na ndị otu Sovereignty Council Aisha Musa el-Said na Raja Nicola
Al-Boushi kọwara nhọpụta ya dị ka "Ministry of the Revolution"
O gosipụtara ịnụ ọkụ n'obi ya maka ọnọdụ ahụ, na-ekwu,

N'abalị iri atọ n'ọnwa Septemba n'afọ 2019, a malitere otu egwuregwu bọọlụ ụmụ nwanyị iri abụọ na otu n'okpuru ozi al-Boushi, ebe al-Bushi na Aisha Musa nọ na egwuregwu dị n'etiti ndị otu Eltahadi na Eldifaa, nke ndị inyom na-ekpe ikpe.
Onye nkwusa Islamist na onye na-akwado onye bụbu onye isi ala Omar al-Bashir, Abdal Hai Youssef, boro al-Boushi ebubo nkwulu na ndapụ n'ezi ofufe maka iweghachi bọọlụ ụmụ nwanyị na Sudan
N'okpuru Nkeji edemede 126.2 nke mbipụta 1991 nke Iwu Mpụ Sudan, a na-ata ndapụ n'ezi ofufe ahụhụ site na ikpe ọnwụ ma ọ bụrụ na onye a na-ebo ebubo echegharịghị
Al-Boushi tinyere akwụkwọ mkpesa megide Youssef
Minista na-ahụ maka ozi Faisal Saleh kwuru na nkwupụta Youssef bụ mwakpo megide ikike ụmụ nwanyị ma kwuo na ndị kansụl Sudan rịọrọ Minista Ikpe Ziri Ezi ka ha mee "ihe iwu dị mkpa" megide Youssef.
